video.title: Dino Squad
video.synopsis: When a group of teens gains the ability to turn into dinosaurs, they use their powers to fight evil foes intent on destroying humankind.

episodes.synopsis: On a field trip to explore tide pools, five of Ms. Moynihan's students are accidentally contaminated with mutated primordial ooze, which turns these ordinary teenagers into extraordinary dinosaur heroes: the Dino Squad!
episodes.title: The Beginning

episodes.synopsis: In his latest experiment, Victor Veloci oozes a plant from the Triassic period. Now, it's up to Rodger to use his human brains and dino brawn to stop the monstrous mutation before it envelops all of Kittery Point.
episodes.title: Growth Potential

episodes.synopsis: Always obsessed with being the center of attention, Caruso auditions for the popular television show "U Famous." But Caruso's quest for fame could cause him to reveal his secret dino identity on national television.
episodes.title: Tangled Web

episodes.synopsis: Although he's only supposed to use his dino powers to do good, Caruso cheats and uses his abilities to win a football contest. But the ultimate victor could be the villainous Veloci, who uses Caruso's dino signature to track down the Dino Squad.
episodes.title: T-Rex Formation

episodes.synopsis: Caruso let the dog out! Now he's got to find Rump and bring him home before the mutant dino dog's merry mayhem demolishes all of Kittery Point... and leads the Dino Squad right into Victor Veloci's clutches.
episodes.title: Who Let the Dog Out?

episodes.synopsis: Punked-out Buzz isn't the bravest guy around, so it's not a big surprise when he's targeted by a school bully. The Dino Squad tries to help Buzz learn how to handle the situation without fighting back.
episodes.title: Bully 4 U

episodes.synopsis: An Internet game takes a dangerous turn when Buzz accidentally reveals personal information about himself and the Dino Squad to a new online friend... and the "friend" turns out to be Victor Veloci in disguise!
episodes.title: The Lost Worldwide Web

episodes.synopsis: When a tabloid TV reporter comes looking for a big story about dinosaurs, Caruso's desperate pursuit of fame puts the entire Dino Squad at risk. Will he keep their powers secret or spill the beans?
episodes.title: Headline Nuisance

episodes.synopsis: Always the prankster, Rodger plays a series of practical jokes on his teammates. But no one's laughing when Victor Veloci shows up. Suddenly, the smart aleck's goofs could spell disaster for the Dino Squad.
episodes.title: Who'll Stop the Rain?

episodes.synopsis: Buzz creates a phony photograph of a rock star dinosaur and sells it to an online bidder. But the fake photo reveals the Dino Squad's real headquarters, and the team has to race to get the photo back before it winds up in Victor Veloci's hands.
episodes.title: Zoom In on Zoom

episodes.synopsis: When Fiona's family vacation is interrupted by an invasion of mutant moles, she calls in the Dino Squad. The mutant encounter is complicated because the team has to do their work without Fiona's folks discovering her secret dino identity.
episodes.title: A Mole Lotta Trouble

episodes.synopsis: Veloci creates a herd of mutant moose-a-saurs, but before the Dino Squad can trap and de-ooze the creatures, the friends must overcome their fears -- real and imagined -- in order to survive a night in the wilderness.
episodes.title: The Not So Great Outdoors

episodes.synopsis: Caruso creates an Internet show about pets, but the show is a disaster. Caruso gives the critters to his dino teammates... which turns into an even bigger disaster when the pets begin to mutate into monster pet-a-sauruses.
episodes.title: Pet Peeve
